lead_paragraph: Carlota Ciganda birdied three of the last six holes Thursday for a 5-under 67 and a share of the lead with playing partner Sarah Jane Smith in the Citibanamex Lorena Ochoa Invitational.

headline.print_headline: Ciganda, Smith Share Lorena Ochoa Invitational Lead
